菱形鑲嵌也可一作為拼花的設計<ref>{{citation|title=Treasure Chests: The Legacy of Extraordinary Boxes|first1=Lon|last1=Schleining|first2=Randy|last2=O'Rourke|publisher=Taunton Press|year=2003|isbn=9781561586516|contribution=Tricking the eyes with tumbling blocks|page=58|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xA91sJ1LNQIC&pg=PA58}}.</ref>、地面或牆面貼磚，有時會在菱形上做些形狀的變化<ref>[http://mathtourist.blogspot.com/2011/02/tessellation-tango.html Tessellation Tango], The Mathematical Tourist, Drexel University, retrieved 2012-05-23.</ref>。

